OL,3,CBristol Airport 'scathing' over Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's subsidy for Cardiff
OL,5,CAirport
OL,7,FLawyers working on behalf of Bristol
OL,8,FAirport have written a scathing letter
OL,9,Fto the Welsh Government demanding they
OL,10,Fprovide more details on how they will
OL,11,Fsubsidise Cardiff Airport with
OL,12,Fhundreds of millions of pounds.
OL,14,FOver the next ten years, Cardiff
OL,15,FAirport is set to receive a #205
OL,16,Fmillion subsidy from the Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment. Lawyers for Bristol
OL,18,FAirport say that since Cardiff's
OL,19,Fnationalisation, the airport has cost
OL,20,Feach household in Wales #286.
