OL,7,FDave Lees, Chief Executive Officer at
OL,8,FBristol Airport, raised concern over
OL,9,Fthe amount of detail the Welsh
OL,10,FGovernment has shared on the public
OL,11,Fsubsidy and how it will be spent `
OL,12,Fdespite the Competition and Markets
OL,13,FAuthority highlighting considerable
OL,14,Fissues, including "unevidenced
OL,15,Fassumptions".
OL,17,FThe Chief Executive of Regional & City
OL,18,FAirports, which is responsible for
OL,19,FBournemouth and Exeter, also
OL,20,Fcriticised the Welsh Government's
OL,21,Fplans.
